                     Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb68" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Wien XVIII</hi></rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb235251"><hi rend="latintype">Hasenauerstr 59</hi></rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p rend="center"><pb facs="1909_AS_RBH_2_00028"/><hi rend="pre-print">D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur Schnitzler</hi></p><p rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi></p><p><pb facs="1909_AS_RBH_2_00029"/>Einladg zur <hi rend="underline" n="1"><rs type="work" ref="#pmb30033" subtype="implied"><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01820-1"/>Generalprobe<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01820-1"><rs ref="#pmb30033" type="work">Anatols Hochzeitsmorgen</rs> wurde am <ref target="1909-01-10" subtype="date-only" type="schnitzler-tagebuch"/> im
                        Zuge einer Matinée gegeben.</note></rs> im <rs ref="#pmb298" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Johann Strauss</hi> Theater</rs></hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><hi rend="underline" n="1"><date>Sam<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag den 9. 1.</date></hi> für Dr. <hi rend="latintype">Richard Beer-Hofmann</hi> und Frau <rs type="person" ref="#pmb10860" subtype="implied">Gemahlin</rs>.</p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="2"><space dim="vertical" unit="line" quantity="1"/><p><seg rend="left"><pb facs="1909_AS_RBH_1_00005"/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><date when="1909-01-07">7. 1. 09</date>.</seg></p><p><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168940">Wien XVIII. Spoettelgasse 7</rs>.</hi></p><p>Dies, lieber Richard genügt u eigentlich brauchen Sie auch das nicht. <rs ref="#pmb30033" type="work" subtype="implied">Beginn</rs> (angeblich)
                  <time>10</time>. Eingang Bühnenthürl. Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr</p><closer><signed>Arthur.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
